title: Multitracks (pack 2)
description:
Here is my second volume of various multitracks in the sound formats FLAC, MP3 and MOGG.

You can use the free software Audacity (http://audacity.sourceforge.net) to open all of these formats, including the MOGG files, which are multitrack OGG files.

Have fun playing around with them - make some great remixes and mashups, or just teach yourself how to mix with the source files of these fantastic recordings.

And PLEASE seed to at least 1:1 or preferably more. If everybody could seed as much as they download, a torrent will never die!
